/*
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  PS-CRM SEED DATA SUMMARY
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  SEEDED TABLES:
  ┌────────────────────────────────┬───────┬──────────────────────────────────┐
  │ Table                          │ Rows  │ Notes                            │
  ├────────────────────────────────┼───────┼──────────────────────────────────┤
  │ cities                         │   1   │ Delhi only                       │
  │ jurisdictions (authority)      │   6   │ MCD NDMC CANTONMENT PWD DDA DJB │
  │ jurisdictions (zones)          │  14   │ All 12 MCD zones + 2 others      │
  │ jurisdictions (wards)          │  10   │ Representative sample w/ WKB     │
  │ departments                    │  11   │ 9 MCD + DJB + PWD               │
  │ infra_types                    │  12   │ Full Delhi taxonomy              │
  │ infra_nodes                    │  35   │ Real GPS coords, all zones       │
  │ workflow_constraints           │   3   │ Monsoon / Smog / Election        │
  │ users                          │   5   │ System agent + dev team          │
  └────────────────────────────────┴───────┴──────────────────────────────────┘

  NOT SEEDED (start fresh):
    complaints, complaint_embeddings, complaint_clusters,
    complaint_cluster_members, workflow_instances,
    workflow_complaints, workflow_template_*, tasks, tenders,
    surveys, notifications, agent_logs, domain_events

  HOW TO USE:
    1. psql -h <host> -U <user> -d <db> -f ps_crm_final.sql   # schema
    2. psql -h <host> -U <user> -d <db> -f ps_crm_seed_data.sql  # this file

  WARD BOUNDARIES:
    Only 10 representative ward polygons are included here.
    To restore all 272 ward boundaries, re-run the COPY block
    from the original 4(1).sql dump on the jurisdictions table.
    Zone-level routing will work for all wards not yet seeded
    (fn_resolve_jurisdiction falls back to the parent zone).

  INFRA TYPE → DEPT MAPPING (default_dept_ids):
    STLIGHT     → EM
    ROAD        → ENGG
    POTHOLE     → ENGG
    DRAIN       → ENGG + DEMS
    FOOTPATH    → ENGG
    TREE        → HORT
    GARBAGE     → PH
    WIRE_HAZARD → EM
    WATER_PIPE  → DJB
    SEWER       → DJB + DEMS
    HOARDING    → ADV
    ELEC_POLE   → EM

══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
*/
